  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dc5\u0dd4 \u0da2\u0dd6\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba: \"\u0db8\u0dd9\u0dba \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd4\u0da7\u0dd4 \u0dc4\u0dd0\u0db8\u0ddd\u0db8\u0da7\u0db8 \u0dc0\u0dda\u0daf\u0db1\u0dcf \u0db6\u0dbb \u0db8\u0dad\u0d9a\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d89\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dbd\u0dcf \u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf\"",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Black Julie: \"This has left a painful memory for everyone who experienced it.\"",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Human rights activists say that justice has not been done for the people who were wronged in Black July 1983.",
        "The 39th Black July celebrations were held in Colombo on July 23rd and 24th.",
        "There, many creative presentations were presented to educate the society about the injustice done to the Tamil people."
      ],
